uplink-mobsyndimothroach-name = Syndimothroach Teleporter
uplink-mobsyndimothroach-desc = Call in a genetically engineered attack mothroach to harass your foes and chew through wires. Their hardened carapace makes them immune to low pressure, but makes subdermal implantation impossible.

uplink-energysabre-name = Energy Sabre
uplink-energysabre-desc = A stylish blade issued to the elite members of Syndicate High Command. Cuts through anything like butter!
